item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: wonster_lab
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.content:encoded:
X home pages template

Dzięki Visual Composerowi możesz stworzyć dowolną stronę główną główną z komponentów dostepnych w Symetrio. Wychodzimy na przeciw Twoim oczekiwaniom i kupując Symetrio możesz wykorzystać jedną z X zdefiniowanych stron głównych. Nie musisz jej budować od 0.

Multi-site allows you to update Symetrio and all instaled plugins with only one administration panel.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_empty_space height="30"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"][/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="MENU PER PAGE" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:26|text_align:left|color:%23000000|line_height:1.0" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1416488045185{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 40px !important;}"][vc_empty_space height="10"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]Symetrio allows you to create different menu on each page, now you can create totally different pages in one WordPress installation[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="full_width" columns_type="wtrMargin" columns_autohight="wtrNoAutoHeightColumns" menu_above="wtrNoAboveMenuRow" bg_type="color" color_bg="#ffffff" img_attr="default" color_overlay_opt="off" color_overlay="rgba(31,206,109,0.6)" parallax="none" type_video="local" animate="none" delay="0"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_empty_space height="30"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_empty_space height="30"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"][/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="SOCIAL MEDIA INTEGRATION" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:26|text_align:left|color:%23000000|line_height:1.0" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1416488105181{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 40px !important;}"][vc_empty_space height="10"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]This theme is big opportunity for your social media debut. Starting from social icons in widgets, buttons and instagram stream in shortcodes to share buttons in blog.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_empty_space height="30"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"][/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="ONE CLICK" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:26|text_align:left|color:%23000000|line_height:1.0" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1416488132798{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 40px !important;}"][vc_empty_space height="10"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]This product include one click option, which allows you to install whole predefined content in just one click, additionally you can choose a different color and mix it.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="full_width" columns_type="wtrMargin" columns_autohight="wtrNoAutoHeightColumns" menu_above="wtrNoAboveMenuRow" bg_type="color" color_bg="#ffffff" img_attr="default" color_overlay_opt="off" color_overlay="rgba(31,206,109,0.6)" parallax="none" type_video="local" animate="none" delay="0"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_empty_space height="30"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_empty_space height="30"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"][/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="CUSTOMIZER" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:26|text_align:left|color:%23000000|line_height:1.0" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1416488858822{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 40px !important;}"][vc_empty_space height="10"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]Change every single colour on page with few clicks. Symetrio uses Customizer that is part of yours WordPress. Modify page with live-view mode. Each change is visible right away.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_empty_space height="30"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"][/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="MULTI GYM LOCATION" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:26|text_align:left|color:%23000000|line_height:1.0" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1416488877092{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 40px !important;}"][vc_empty_space height="10"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]Symetrio supports presenting informactions based on gym location. You can create advanced filters that will connect Trainers / Classes / Class Rooms / Events with one exact location or group. With this function you can create schedules for specified location. Present personel from specified location. [/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="full_width" columns_type="wtrMargin" columns_autohight="wtrNoAutoHeightColumns" menu_above="wtrNoAboveMenuRow" bg_type="color" color_bg="#ffffff" img_attr="default" color_overlay_opt="off" color_overlay="rgba(31,206,109,0.6)" parallax="none" type_video="local" animate="none" delay="0"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_empty_space height="30"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_empty_space height="30"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"][/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="EVENT PAGE" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:26|text_align:left|color:%23000000|line_height:1.0" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1416489204292{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 40px !important;}"][vc_empty_space height="10"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]You can define organizators and event locations, by that you won`t need to define many times same groups for upcoming events.  We are ahead of your expectations, you don`t need to search for plugins that will allow you to do that. Exclusively for Symetrio we designed module that fits perfectly website.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_empty_space height="30"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"][/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="MENU BELOW" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:26|text_align:left|color:%23000000|line_height:1.0" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1416489226758{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 40px !important;}"][vc_empty_space height="10"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]Your header can be unique, and all of this with showing content above the menu bar. Just pick whatever you want and place it on top. Dosen`t matter if you want to use HTML code or Symetrio shortcodes, both will work perfectly. How the header will look like is on you and your creativity.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="full_width" columns_type="wtrMargin" columns_autohight="wtrNoAutoHeightColumns" item.title: Changelog
item.dc:creator: wonster_lab
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row row_type="boxed" columns_type="wtrMargin" columns_autohight="wtrNoAutoHeightColumns" menu_above="wtrNoAboveMenuRow" el_class="wtrChangelog" bg_type="color" color_bg="#ffffff" img_attr="default" color_overlay_opt="off" color_overlay="rgba(31,206,109,0.6)" parallax="none" type_video="local" animate="none" delay="0"][vc_column width="1/6"][vc_empty_space height="50px"][vc_wtr_button url="url:http%3A%2F%2Fthemes.wonster.co%2Fsymetrio%2F|title:Go%20to%20home|" label="Go back" align="left" size="normal" color="c_blue" corner="wtrButtonRad" background="wtrButtonNoTrans" animate_icon="wtrButtonHoverNoAnim" full_width="wtrButtonNoFullWidth" margin_left="10" margin_right="0" margin_top="0" margin_bottom="0" animate="none" delay="0"][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_empty_space height="60px"][vc_custom_heading text="Symetrio changelog" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:26|text_align:left|color:%23000000|line_height:1.0" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]
After every theme update you have to reinstall all plugins included with symetrio theme.

Version 2.1

(Tuesday, 20 Jan 2015)
  • [fix] translation for Countdown shortcode
  • [fix] translation for Schedule module
  • [fix] issues with class schedule in multi week mode
  • [fix] issues with class schedule for mobile view
  • [fix] issues with class page for mobile view
  • PO/MO files improvements

Version 2.0

(Tuesday, 20 Jan 2015)
  • [add] - integration with pricing table plugin Easy Pricing Tables Lite by Fatcat Apps - https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-pricing-tables/
  • [add] - new color scheme - Martial - arts
  • [add] - new Demo - Martial - arts
  • [add] - new facebook like box widget
  • [add] - attribute link for icon shortcode
  • [fix] - Optimisation for Wonster Shortcodes for Visual Composer - Symetrio Edition
  • [fix] - issues with excerpt field for news shortcode
  • [fix] - issues with new classes for column shortcode
  • [fix] - issues with divivder shortcode
  • [fix] - Hiding search search input for mobile navigation
  • [fix] - Customizer imrpvements
  • [fix] - issues with Class Schedule in multi-week module
  • [fix] - issues with centered background in class page for Firefox
  • [fix] - PO/MO update
  • [fix] - Target "_blank" for instagram gallery link
  • [fix] - Target "_blank" for social media elements

Version 1.2.1

(Tuesday, 13 Jan 2015)
  • [fix] - Events review: http://themes.wonster.co/symetrio/events-stream/
  • [fix] - Upcoming events - widget
  • [fix] - Events - widget
  • [fix] - Events - shortcode
  • [fix] - Pagination
  • [fix] - Translator improvement
  • [new] - Option tab in Classes Schedule

Version 1.2

(Thursday, 8 Jan 2015)
  • [fix] - target link in IconBox shortcode
  • [fix] - problem with displaying coaches list in class detail
  • [fix] - error with saving in Theme Options panel
  • [fix] - problem with long event name in Event shortcode
  • [new] - woocomerce recent products shortcode
  • [new] - option that allows to hide difficulty level in class page
  • [new] - option that allows to hide difficulty level in class shortcode
  • [new] - trainer sorting option in class page - the order determined by the attribute "order" in trainer admin page
  • [new] - option that allows to hide empty space (hours in which there is no scheduled classes) in Schedule shortcode

Version 1.1

(TUESDAY, 30 Dec 2014)
  • Improved speed of plugins
  • Improved speed of theme
  • Removed errors from theme settings

Version 1.0.3

(Monday, 22 Dec 2014)
  • Speed improvements
  • Plugins update
  • WordPress 4.1 Compatible

Version 1.0.2

(Monday, 8 Dec 2014)
  • Fixed: display bug with main navigation on Safari (Windows)

Version 1.0.1

(Thursday, 4 Dec 2014)
  • Navigation improvements
  • Theme options improvements

Version 1.0.0

(Wednesday, 3 Dec 2014)
  • Initial release
[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="30px"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][/vc_row]
